\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0
\fs28 \cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Today I want to tell you a story of a guy who seem to be doing everything right\'85
\fs24 \uc0\u8232 \
\ls2\ilvl0
\fs28 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 His name is Paul and if you know the story\'85he had an incredible interaction with God that changed his life forever.
\fs24 \uc0\u8232 \
\ls2\ilvl0
\fs28 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 This guy would become famous and change the church forever\'85but not because where he started but where ended up.
\fs24 \uc0\u8232 \
\ls2\ilvl0
\fs28 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 In the beginning this guy was an evangelist\'85he would go from place to place as a tent maker/pastor.
\fs24 \uc0\u8232 \
\ls2\ilvl0
\fs28 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 He would show up and start churches all over the world\'85but again\'85that isn\'92t what he\'92s famous for.
\fs24 \uc0\u8232 \
\ls2\ilvl0
\fs28 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 There is even this book that chronicle part of his life\'85the book of acts gives us some background about all of this stories.
\fs24 \uc0\u8232 \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl1
\fs28 \cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 He was incredibly successful it seems wherever he went.
\fs24 \uc0\u8232 \
\ls2\ilvl1
\fs28 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 And so he developed this reputation and he would write this letters sometimes to people and churches.
\fs24 \uc0\u8232 \
\ls2\ilvl1
\fs28 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 We have some of them
\fs24 \uc0\u8232 \
\ls2\ilvl1
